{"tid":1525713,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[到港鐵還] Byebuyday行動升級 - 一人一信詢問港鐵租戶會否停租","createTime":"2019-09-01T02:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T11:10:06.000Z","uid":58883,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d46aad16d82cccb58e864b4d46932072d613cf8e","tid":1525713,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:30:29.000Z","msg":"大家之前都可以聽過我地日五罷買/全民罷買日。<br />\n<br />\n我地一眾Byebuyer對港鐵與黑警<span style=\"color: navy;\">同流合污</span>，一次又一次放任黑社會進入車箱無差別攻擊市民，深感痛心疾首。因此，我地決定將<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">行動升級</span></strong></span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">我地一眾議工用左一晚時間去整合港鐵站內商户既Contact List（<em>一共審視左１千多間店</em>）</span>，希望大家可以每一出多一份力，用租金收入去比壓力垃圾港鐵（大家可能唔知租金佔左港鐵利潤<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">５０％</span></strong>）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/70293387_122647052427081_7347680653854375936_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQlkGBaMbQ2awxeig5Jxw60_JxcB_D0KBz0TdvftzQ3CGjdZI2Lh4goELFjk3sH8468&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=e796c949a452ec5a04d3216135f1c7ce&amp;oe=5DCE4998\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F70293387_122647052427081_7347680653854375936_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQlkGBaMbQ2awxeig5Jxw60_JxcB_D0KBz0TdvftzQ3CGjdZI2Lh4goELFjk3sH8468%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3De796c949a452ec5a04d3216135f1c7ce%26oe%3D5DCE4998&h=9e28b460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>第一階段行動內容：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一人一信詢問站內租戶是否會停止租約</span></strong></span>，我地目的係要佢地１０天內公開回應，否則如果佢地唔會撤回租約，我地會將結果／名單整文宣列出黎<br />\nＡ. 如店鋪有Email，一人一信詢問租戶是否會停止租約（建議一次過mass email, cc/bcc全部店鋪）； <br />\nＢ. 如店鋪只有Facebook，去店舖Facebook留言<br />\n<br />\n港鐵站內店鋪Email/Facebook清單（有篩選過）：<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1o3xFMh_c0R2Hb2qrDtZtyqXCkBAUXgoTR0RfgTh-UFM/edit#gid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1o3xFMh_c0R2Hb2qrDtZtyqXCkBAUXgoTR0RfgTh-UFM%2Fedit%23gid%3D0&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b0UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=b357c9d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1o3xFMh_c0R2Hb2qrDtZtyqXCkBAUXgoTR0RfgTh-UFM/edit#gid=0</a><br />\n___________________________________________________________<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">查詢信範本:</span></span><br />\n敬啟者：<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於7月21日，8月11及31日港鐵發生嚴重傷人事件，將來港鐵站內／轄下商場如果再次遭受無差別恐怖襲擊時，我們對港鐵公司處理此類事件的應變能力有所保留。故本人來函欲查詢 貴公司會否於短期內檢視停止／放棄所有港鐵站內／商場之租約，以保障職員及顧客安全。<br />\n<br />\n如 貴公司在１０天之內沒有答覆，本人將視 貴公司於未來將會繼續於港鐵商場的租約和營運。<br />\n<br />\n敬希回覆，祝<br />\n鈞安<br />\n<br />\n小市民XXX謹啟<br />\n__________________________________________________________<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>第二階段行動內容：</strong></span><br />\n我地仲準備左一份名單針對港鐵<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">商場</span></span>，但因為太多租戶，未夠人手去做。所以如果大家有心可以用以下Ｇoogle sheet去幫手搵商戶Contact List，如果完成到就會發起第２波<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><br />\nFb Link: shorturl.at/rHQR7<br />\n記得LIKE埋我地FB去接受最新罷買資訊</strong></span>"},{"pid":"c2685af5e567a61f99e025f8b1681c1f15ed9857","tid":1525713,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:30:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721/831無獎問答遊戲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">試分辨以上事件</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqzkvvH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqzkvvH.jpg&h=849fcb35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月，機場見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"87c5a5378ef85f24cf3c82edd437a1c418304e50","tid":1525713,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:31:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69441021_122627725762347_1384027076260003840_n.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQmKXRiK3A6kmrcbntfUlo17IDGiqkmXjMeTIunIfNmZvNNSQ-8DQw_Jp4cBX_CMjJk&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=f780bb678e91040643cdcac65a1a07b6&amp;oe=5E003FCD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69441021_122627725762347_1384027076260003840_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQmKXRiK3A6kmrcbntfUlo17IDGiqkmXjMeTIunIfNmZvNNSQ-8DQw_Jp4cBX_CMjJk%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Df780bb678e91040643cdcac65a1a07b6%26oe%3D5E003FCD&h=8caced30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35169373298ce1b93f2835dce492fe9426d55c68","tid":1525713,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69551763_10157867324515016_6641357884569419776_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQmeDcetWo0MlvGZHP6HaqwPcSaVMolOuacweRVSg-_wLHR8WPlm_PZMS6bIqdUwkBc&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=c7815288ab5462fc3e70f39bcbe48ac0&amp;oe=5E0D986C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69551763_10157867324515016_6641357884569419776_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQmeDcetWo0MlvGZHP6HaqwPcSaVMolOuacweRVSg-_wLHR8WPlm_PZMS6bIqdUwkBc%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Dc7815288ab5462fc3e70f39bcbe48ac0%26oe%3D5E0D986C&h=e67810c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afa7215e67bf507ca6fb4d3