e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:33:05.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QG5GZ57.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQG5GZ57.gif&h=70f70c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQ6rr7H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQ6rr7H.gif&h=2e882f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b236ae277f318107bb85a047254ca8e60d8a90cb","tid":1525713,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:33:07.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"7585b206810d285a3ec07286ccc819a4cb05308c","tid":1525713,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:33:23.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"649ecf30f4395ad87977dbe888b4db1ce1c32215","tid":1525713,"uid":50006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:33:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79959ea5fd47a32e225a519ee8c981bbc77ca5bf","tid":1525713,"uid":58883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:34:35.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"b72dc23e85d004d0fbff017352a7068a20fb536b","tid":1525713,"uid":299694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:34:45.000Z","msg":"唔坐唔買不消費, 大家一獲熟"},{"pid":"e9a26bf59dbaf2c385998fa6c56e7ffeeb1f7324","tid":1525713,"uid":143382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:35:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98dd061f6c8eae61e8c6164239123c451513d0c1","tid":1525713,"uid":58883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:36:00.000Z","msg":"咪撚再係減鐵站內買野,7-11都唔站先"},{"pid":"9ff3e363944403ac68b55d0e0e2da2789f0c86e4","tid":1525713,"uid":58883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:36:20.000Z","msg":"咪撚再係減鐵站內/商場買野,搵7-11買支水都出站先"},{"pid":"3c9c90bfdbc8d3d46cf04f39f7139b4fed5fb7